## 1. Scope & board context

This documents the estimator architecture generically, grounded in the source at the commit above. On the **`armada-ctrl-zero-h7-oem`** board the wired sensors are 3 IMUs (BMI088, ICM-20602, ICM-20948 â€” the last with an AK09916 magnetometer), a barometer, and external GNSS; see `imu_clarification_2026-05-14.*` for the driver/topic detail this builds on. EKF2 only ever sees the *aggregated* uORB topics (`vehicle_imu`, `vehicle_magnetometer`, `vehicle_air_data`, `sensor_gps`, â€¦), never the raw `sensor_*` driver topics.

